      "text": "# returned context (fits max_tokens)\nGOAL: Survey 2026 sparse attention methods\n\nRECENT TURNS:\n  [user]  try longformer next\n  [agent] queried arxiv, 4 papers found\n\nRELEVANT HISTORY:\n  [decision] prioritise papers with code\n  [fact]     BigBird = O(n) attention\n  [tool]     arxiv.search(\"sparse attention\")",
